I'm using generators just for the example, thats not related to the variable scoping.

``` javascript
function* foo() {
  let response;
  try {
    response = yield request({});
  } // ...
}
```

``` javascript
function* foo() {
  try {
    var response = yield request({});
  } // ...
}
```

